# Color Utilities

ANSI color codes for terminal output.

@text red(text) = [[[31m{{text}}[0m]]
@text green(text) = [[[32m{{text}}[0m]]
@text yellow(text) = [[[33m{{text}}[0m]]
@text blue(text) = [[[34m{{text}}[0m]]
@text bold(text) = [[[1m{{text}}[0m]]
